# Go Test Standards

Go-specific additions to **test-standards** for `*_test.go` files.

## Naming

- Outer `Test` name: `Test` + PascalCase of symbol under test, no underscores
  (e.g. `TestValidateLogSpec`, `TestCappValidatorHandle`).
